divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: Me and two friends were in a hot tub outside my house around 7:30 pm when one of them looked up and noticed some weird lights. At first we thought it was the tram going up the mountain, but it was too high for that. Then we thought it had to be a plane, but it wasn t moving. And it wasnt a star because it was 4 blinking lights kind of moving around. Then, all of the sudden it zoomed off at an unbelievable speed, making a LUEEEEEEEEEEEEEE sound. I thought it was kind of weird, as I don t believe in supernatural occurances, but I thought I should send it to someone because there is a high-tech military airforce a few miles away, and it might be worthy to look into. Thanks, Tyler
